RELEASE OF MECHANIC'S AND MATERIALMAN'S LIEN KNOW ALL MEN BY THESE PRESENTS
DE MEĞİ
STATE OF TEXAS-
COUNTY OF TRAVIS
On December 09, 2020 files and recorded that certain Affidavit for Mechanic's and Materialman's Lien (the "Affidavit"), was
recorded under Clerk's Pile No. £ 2020238700, of the Official Public Records of Travis County, Texas, wherein, AMERICAN
BUILDERS AND CONTRACTORS SUPPLY CO ., INC. - ABC SUPPLY CO ., INC. is the Claimant, KM SWEETWATER LLC
and/or NASH SWEETWATER LLC is the Owner of the real property described therein, and sald lien being in the amount of
Eleven Thousand Eight Hundred and Twenty Eight Dollars and Twelve Cents ($11,828.12), for labor, material and/or equipment
furnished by Claimant (the "Claim") to improve the real property commonly known as 18101 State Hwy 71 Bldg A, Austin, Texas
78738, Travis County, Texas, and being-more particularly described hereto and incorporated hercin by reference for all purposes
as follows:
(See attached document) LOT 1 BLK B SWEETWATER CENTRE PHS ONE LOT 2 BLK B SWEETWATER CENTRE PHS
ONE LOT 4 BLK B SWEETWATER CENTRE PHS ONE.ABS 2245 SUR 61 HALLMAN E, ABS 42 SUR 31 BEATY &
MOULTON A ACR 10.000 (1-D-1W).ABS 1025 SUR 527 WILDY S 3.709 AC ABS 800 SUR 527 WILDY S ACR 16.198 (1-D-
1W) ABS 2679 SUR 86 BARLOW W A & ABS 1025 SUR 527 WILDY S & VAR SURS ACR 49.4676 (1-D-1W) ABS 2679 SUR
86 BARLOW W A & ABS 1025 SUR 527 WILDY S & VAR SURS ACR 111.4695 (1-D-1W) UNT 1 SWEETWATER LOT 5
COMMERCIAL CONDOMINIUMS PLUS 50.0 % INT IM COM AREA
For and in consideration of the total sum of Elever-Thousand Fight Hundred and Twenty Eight Dollars and Twelve Cents
($11,828.12), the receipt and sufficiency of which is hereby acknowledged, Claimant does hereby fully, finally and completely
walve, release, discharge and exonerate KM SWEETWATER,LLC andfor NASH SWEETWATER LLC , FIVE STAR ROOFING ,
(collectively the "Released Parties"), and the Project of and from any and all claims, liabilities, demands, liens, rights to claim
liens, rights, equities and/or causes of action of any kind-whatsoever which the Claimant has, had or may be entitled to assert on
account of materials supplied, labor furnished and/or Equipment sold or rented for the construction of the Project, including but
not limited to any lien or bond claim filed by Claimant.
Claimant warrants and represents to the Released Parties that the subcontractors, suppliers, laborers and/or lessors of
construction equipment that have supplied labor, materials, and/or equipment to the Claimant in connection with the Project have
been paid in full. Claimant further agrees to indemnity, defend and hald harmless the Released Parties of and from any and all
claims, liabilities, demands, damages or costs, Including attorneys' fees and expenses, which the Released Parties may incur by
virtue of the Claimant's failure to pay any of its subcontractors, suppliers, laborers and/or lessors of construction equipment in
connection with the Project.
AMERICAN BUILDERS AND CONTRACTORS SUPPLY CO ., INC. - ABO SUPPLY CO ., INC.
106 Decker Court, Suite 100
Irving, Texas 75062
(972) 281/4546
By:
Ariela Wagner, Agent
STATE OF FLORIDA
COUNTY OF BROWARD
BEFORE ME, the undersigned Notary Public, on this day personally appeared, Ariela Wagner, Agent of AMERICAN BUILDERS
AND CONTRACTORS SUPPLY CO ., INC. - ABC SUPPLY CO ., INC ., known to me to be the person whose name is
subscribed to the foregoing instrument, who acknowledged to me that he executed the same for the purposes
and consideration therein expressed and in the capacity therein stated as the act and deed of sald corporation
and further swore that the foregoing was tye and correct. Given under my hand and seal of office, and sworn to
on this_
BARBI SCHOPPERT
MY COMMISSION # HH 068734
Notary Public
EXPIRES: December 17, 2024
Bonded Thru Notary Public Underwellers
AFTER RECORDING RETURNING TO:
